 >>>>>>>settings.py
 
1)BASE_DIR--> is a variabe which contains abspath pf base directory/project folder
2)SECRET_KEY-->This adds a seret key to every django project.
3)DEBUG=TRUE/FALSE ---->
	DEVELOPENT -->TRUE,DEPLOYMENT-->Flase{allow host }
4)ALLOWED_HOST=[*]
	A list of strings representing the host/domain
5)INSTALLED_APPS=[]
	WRITE ALL THE APP NAMES {NO DUPLICATES}
6)TEMPLATES=[]



>>>>>>>HOW TO RUN SERVER
python manage.py runserver {portnumber eg5555}
python manage.py runserver


